headline: HUMAIN AND ADOBE ANNOUNCE GLOBAL STRATEGIC PARTNERSHIP TO BUILD AI MODELS AND AI-POWERED APPLICATIONS TUNED FOR THE ARAB WORLD AT THE U.S.-SAUDI INVESTMENT FORUM
summary: HUMAIN, a PIF company delivering global full-stack artificial intelligence solutions, and Adobe (Nasdaq: ADBE), a world leading creative and marketing software company, announced its partnership today at the U.S.-Saudi Investment Forum. The global partnership is set to redefine how cultural intelligence, creative tools, and AI infrastructure come together.
